ly!  @tarte cosmetics “Tartelette in bloom” clay eyeshadow palette 🧸  - #tartecosmetics #tarte #tarteeyeshadow #eyeshadow #makeup #beauty #fyp #fallmakeup #ultafinds #viralvideo #favoritemakeup #pinterest ', author='marisalxo'), VideoModel(video_id='7326839023308197126', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@justjasneet/video/7326839023308197126', description='🤍 DIOR 🤍 This palette is so perfect I had to have it!! It has everyday neutrals and smokier shades. It’s perfect to throw into your everyday makeup bag. The formula isn’t super pigmented like Pat McGrath or Natasha Denona for example. It’s a soft elegant formula, which is why I think it’s good for everyday. If you were doing your makeup in a rush I don’t really think you’ll mess up because the shades are pretty foolproof, except the black shade which packs more of a punch. Overall I’m super happy with this as it’s my first eyeshadow palette from the backstage line! I got mine directly from the Dior website if you’re interested!  🤍 What are your thoughts? 🤍 . . . . . . . . . #diorbeauty #diorbackstage #dioreyeshadow #diorsmokyessentials #luxurybeauty #luxeliving #newmakeup  Dior beauty, luxury makeup, smoky essentials ', author='justjasneet'), VideoModel(video_id='7324393390559251755', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@makeupbymario/video/7324393390559251755', description='our #etherealeyes palette ✨ was so good we had to bring it back. In stock at @sephora & makeupbymario.com! swatches by @Thaothanhnn ', author='makeupbymario'), VideoModel(video_id='7494766166808743190', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@aestheticdrafts24/video/7494766166808743190', description='UGC Beauty @Diorbeauty  Hey Brands, if you’re looking for a UGC creator to create content for your Brand, then look no further 👀 Email me now for inquiry 🩷 #diorpalette #diorbeauty #dioreyeshadow #ugcbeauty #ugcbeautycontentcreator #ugccontentcreator #ugcexample #ugcbranddeals #ugcbrands #ugccollab #ugccollaboration ', author='aestheticdrafts24'), VideoModel(video_id='73