ly!  @tarte cosmetics “Tartelette in bloom” clay eyeshadow palette 🧸  - #tartecosmetics #tarte #tarteeyeshadow #eyeshadow #makeup #beauty #fyp #fallmakeup #ultafinds #viralvideo #favoritemakeup #pinterest ', author='marisalxo'), VideoModel(video_id='7326839023308197126', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@justjasneet/video/7326839023308197126', description='🤍 DIOR 🤍 This palette is so perfect I had to have it!! It has everyday neutrals and smokier shades. It’s perfect to throw into your everyday makeup bag. The formula isn’t super pigmented like Pat McGrath or Natasha Denona for example. It’s a soft elegant formula, which is why I think it’s good for everyday. If you were doing your makeup in a rush I don’t really think you’ll mess up because the shades are pretty foolproof, except the black shade which packs more of a punch. Overall I’m super happy with this as it’s my first eyeshadow palette from the backstage line! I got mine directly from the Dior website if you’re interested!  🤍 What are your thoughts? 🤍 . . . . . . . . . #diorbeauty #diorbackstage #dioreyeshadow #diorsmokyessentials #luxurybeauty #luxeliving #newmakeup  Dior beauty, luxury makeup, smoky essentials ', author='justjasneet'), VideoModel(video_id='7324393390559251755', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@makeupbymario/video/7324393390559251755', description='our #etherealeyes palette ✨ was so good we had to bring it back. In stock at @sephora & makeupbymario.com! swatches by @Thaothanhnn ', author='makeupbymario'), VideoModel(video_id='7494766166808743190', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@aestheticdrafts24/video/7494766166808743190', description='UGC Beauty @Diorbeauty  Hey Brands, if you’re looking for a UGC creator to create content for your Brand, then look no further 👀 Email me now for inquiry 🩷 #diorpalette #diorbeauty #dioreyeshadow #ugcbeauty #ugcbeautycontentcreator #ugccontentcreator #ugcexample #ugcbranddeals #ugcbrands #ugccollab #ugccollaboration ', author='aestheticdrafts24'), VideoModel(video_id='7350432506929335595', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@makeupbymario/video/7350432506929335595', description="In case you weren't sure which Master Mattes® Eyeshadow Palette you need (it's both) 😉 #MasterMattesNeutrals #MakeupByMario", author='makeupbymario'), VideoModel(video_id='7571457432442916099', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@vivian.zhou_/video/7571457432442916099', description='Love it so much 😍 A perfect combination of lighter & darker, nude & rose, and matte & shimmery shades 🥰 Maledives, Hawaii & Necker Island are my favourites.  #makeuppalettes #eyeshadow #tartelette #nudeeyeshadow #eyemakeup ', author='vivian.zhou_'), VideoModel(video_id='7331410761903770886', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@makeupbyjessbrown/video/7331410761903770886', description='3 MUST HAVE DRUGSTORE NEUTRAL EYESHADOW PALETTES 🤑 These formulas are all stunning, and the fact that these are from the drugstore is a bonus 🔥  Please note: I am 31, female, I recently gave birth, my skin is very dry, and I live in Canada. Take these factors into consideration when going on my recommendations 🫶 • Eyeshadow palette - @NYX Cosmetics Canada ultimate warm neutrals shadow palette  • Eyeshadow palette - @Makeup Revolution fundamental reloaded shadow palette   • Eyeshadow palette - @elfcosmetics perfect 10 eyeshadow palette in shade “nude mood” #drugstore #drugstoremakeup #drugstoreeyeshadow #drugstoreeyeshadows #drugstoreeyeshadowpalette #drugstoreshadowpalette #nyxcosmetics #nyxcosmeticscanada #makeuprevolution #revolution #elfcosmetics #shoppersbeauty #walmart #notsponsored ', author='makeupbyjessbrown'), VideoModel(video_id='7347441771204349227', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@not_another_hanna/video/7347441771204349227', description='Welcome to my new series! Where I recommend makeup to elevate your looks and bring you into the editorial world. Editorial recommendations?? Haha idk still working on the name for the series. What do we think?! #beauty #makeup #makeuprecomendation #editorialmakeup #makeupbyma